# Sonoff LAN

Library to interact with Sonoff devices through LAN mode (without eWeLink cloud) with firmware
version 3+ (tested up to version 3.7.x).

Author: Danilo Treffiletti <urban82@gmail.com>

License: BSD-3

Version: 0.4.0

## Install

### Requirements
* Python 3.10+

## Usage
Install with
```pip install sonofflan```

Basic utility
```python -m sonofflan```

